userProfile.about:
We are a young dynamic team which brought together a common passion for travelling, Airbnb hosting, design and desire to do things right plus with FUN!  
 
We are the team behind your stay. From your booking until leaving Prague filled with emotions and experiences it's us taking care of your accommodation, which won't downgrade your experience but shoot it through the roof.  
But who are we? We are a team full of passionate travellers bored with superficial holiday resorts and fabricated touristic attractions. We like coming up with various ways how to improve your stay and turn it into a positive experience that you will remember. We are aware how important the travelling is for you and how much discovering new places means to you. We understand the each of our guests are also customers that always appreciate getting something extra for their money.
 
We love experiencing new things and meeting new people, appreciating good quality of living and seeing new cities/places genuinely and with fun. We want the same for you.

Jakub and his friend, simply great guests. Communication went fluidly. They left apartment in top condition, clean and tidy.
Can't wait to host them again! Highly recommend.

Jakub was a delightful guest, really quiet, polite & easy to get along with. He was very understanding when I had an issue with something in my house & very helpful with a few things. He left the space in a really good condition. I would recommend Jakub as a guest.
